# 🌳 Turtle Recursive Tree

## 🖥️ About this Project
This project uses Python's **turtle module** to create a **recursive tree**. The tree grows using recursion, changing colors as it branches.

## 📦 Installation
To run this project, you need **Python** installed.

1. Clone this repository:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/YourUsername/TurtleTreeProject.git
Navigate to the project folder:
sh
Copy
Edit
cd TurtleTreeProject
Run the script:
sh
Copy
Edit
python tree.py
🚀 Features
Recursive branching for natural tree-like growth
Color-changing branches for better visualization
Turtle graphics for fun animations
